        <div class="content-body">
          <p>A strong IELTS score is the gateway to studying at top universities around the world. Grant Consulting offers structured IELTS preparation courses designed to help students achieve the band scores required by their target institutions. Our classes cover all four sections of the exam — Listening, Reading, Writing, and Speaking — with a curriculum built around proven test-taking strategies and real exam materials.</p>
          <p>Regular practice testing is at the core of our preparation approach. Students take full-length mock exams under timed conditions throughout the course, allowing them to track their progress and identify the specific areas where they need the most improvement. After each practice test, our instructors provide detailed feedback with actionable advice on how to gain additional points in each section.</p>
          <p>The Speaking section is often the most challenging for students in Uzbekistan, and it is the area where personalized coaching makes the biggest difference. Our instructors conduct one-on-one speaking practice sessions that simulate the real exam environment, helping students build fluency, improve pronunciation, and develop the confidence to perform at their best. Whether you need to reach a 6.0 or a 7.5, we tailor our approach to your current level and target score.</p>
        </div>

